# XFlickr architecture

Read [`AGENTS.md`](../../AGENTS.md) and skill [`ai/skills/form-request-service-repository/SKILL.md`](../../ai/skills/form-request-service-repository/SKILL.md).

Flow: `HTTP Request → Controller → FormRequest → Service → Repository → Model`

Artisan: `Command → Service → Repository → Model`. Jobs → Service only.

Services **must not** call Eloquent directly — only Repositories (prefer model scopes). Commands → Services only. Jobs must not use `Model::query()`.

Guard test (Crawler): `Modules/Crawler/tests/Unit/Architecture/CrawlerLayeringTest`.

- Crawl logic: `Modules/Crawler` (`Modules\Crawler\*`) only — do not reimplement fetchers
- Spider mode: opt-in (`spider.enabled` runtime config); see `SpiderPlannerService` and `docs/02-user-guide/spider-mode.md`
- Auth module owns session login/logout + password reset (`Modules/Auth`)
- Dedicated FormRequest required on every mutating action (including body-less logout)

